the tickets in secret.

36
00:01:58,921 --> 00:02:00,488
Arrangements could be made.

37
00:02:00,523 --> 00:02:02,089
Just pick a date
and ring me up.

38
00:02:04,092 --> 00:02:06,127
I have to warn you,
I'm from a small town

39
